      <title>由于 Sambas 和 Yeezys 需求强劲，阿迪达斯上调预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/adidas-raises-forecast-amid-strong-demand-for-sambas-and-yeezys</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 Samba 等经典运动鞋的需求飙升，以及 Yeezy 鞋类库存减少导致销量增加，阿迪达斯公司三个月内第二次上调了利润目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/adidas-raises-forecast-amid-strong-demand-for-sambas-and-yeezys</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 16:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
